title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Crowd Surfing Baby
description: Selena Gomez says she is lucky to be alive in the new trailer for her documentary, and Dwayne Johnson thinks it’s great when people let their infant child crowd surf across a sea of people just to get a photo with him.
